sentences: Gardy Girault (French pronunciation: ​[ɡaʁdi ʒiʁo]), stylized as G∆rdy Gir∆ult, is a Haitian electronic musician, DJ, remixer and record producer.
He is a pioneer of an electronic music subgenre called rara tech that fuses the Afro-Haitian genre rara with house music.
Gardy Girault, is a rare breed in his genre of music.
Driven by his passion of electronic music alive, he integrates ancestral elements native to his land, creating a unique yet contemporary musical experience.
Girault was born in Port-au-Prince, Haiti.
His album Kiskeya was released in 2015.
